---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Digital Signage System â€“ Bryce Kennedy">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-20">
    <!-- Back Navigation -->
    <a 
      href="/#projects" 
      class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-300 hover:text-brand-orange transition-colors mb-8"
    >
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <path d="m15 18-6-6 6-6"/>
      </svg>
      Back to projects
    </a>

    <!-- Project Header -->
    <header class="space-y-4 mb-12">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs mb-4">
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-dark/50 rounded">React</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-dark/50 rounded">Real-time</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-dark/50 rounded">CMS</span>
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold">Digital Signage System</h1>
      
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300">
        Built and maintained a high-visibility digital signage platform serving thousands of displays across the enterprise.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- Project Content -->
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Overview</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          Designed and implemented a comprehensive digital signage platform that powers displays in airports, 
          offices, and operational facilities across American Airlines' global network.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Challenge</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          The organization needed a scalable solution that could:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-300 ml-4">
          <li>Deliver real-time content updates to thousands of displays</li>
          <li>Support multiple content types (video, images, live data feeds)</li>
          <li>Provide non-technical users with an intuitive content management interface</li>
          <li>Handle network disruptions gracefully with offline caching</li>
          <li>Ensure 99.9% uptime for mission-critical displays</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Solution</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          I architected and built the platform with the following key features:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-300 ml-4">
          <li>React-based content player with optimized rendering</li>
          <li>Custom CMS with drag-and-drop scheduling interface</li>
          <li>WebSocket-based real-time content distribution</li>
          <li>Progressive Web App for offline functionality</li>
          <li>Comprehensive monitoring and analytics dashboard</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Results</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300">
          The platform successfully serves content to over 3,000 displays globally, with an average uptime 
          exceeding 99.95%. Content authors can schedule and update displays in real-time, and the system 
          processes over 10 million content impressions monthly.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Technologies Used</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface-card border border-gray-dark/70 rounded-full text-sm">React</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface-card border border-gray-dark/70 rounded-full text-sm">Node.js</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface-card border border-gray-dark/70 rounded-full text-sm">WebSocket</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface-card border border-gray-dark/70 rounded-full text-sm">PWA</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface-card border border-gray-dark/70 rounded-full text-sm">Redis</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-surface-card border border-gray-dark/70 rounded-full text-sm">PostgreSQL</span>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
